snippet.title: Pokémon Saiph 2 - Launch Trailer (Full Game Available!)
snippet.description:
The final release of Pokémon Saiph 2 has been finally finished!
The Vytroverse continues with its 3rd part!
I would like to thank you all for the support you have given me to continue working on this project.
Download the romhack here:
https://www.pokecommunity.com/threads/pok%C3%A9mon-saiph-2-the-vytroverse-part-3-full-game-v1-3-1-final-major-update-available.458509/

The series' discord server, join for updates and to join the VytroVerse Community!
https://discord.gg/dpqNwfw

Sors 2 Teaser:
https://youtu.be/1GnbymvLNRA

Sors 2 Site:
https://www.pokecommunity.com/threads/pok%C3%A9mon-sors-2-the-vytroverse-part-4-wip.526108/

Art in the intro made by azazelamerimonton!
Special thanks for that.

Song used: 
https://youtu.be/6MvENj6yW-A

#Vytron #PokemonSaiph2 #VytroVerse
